<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>The Linux Luminarium</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- 默认跳转到中文版根目录 -->
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=zh/">
    <script>
        (function () {
            // 作为 meta refresh 的补充，在部分浏览器中更可靠
            var target = 'zh/';
            var query = window.location.search || '';
            var hash = window.location.hash || '';
            try {
                window.location.replace(target + query + hash);
            } catch (e) {
                window.location.href = target + query + hash;
            }
        })();
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <noscript>
        <p>正在跳转到中文版… 如果没有自动跳转，请点击
            <a href="zh/">这里进入中文首页</a>。
        </p>
    </noscript>
</body>
</html>

